card.name: CW - Rescission not sent to bureaus

data.text:
@gillianoberholzer 

Is that image from the Attorney System?
The record was Verified in the new CourtWorks system on "2014-08-20 10:36:31.363" but not extracted to Bureaus as there is no ID Number added.

The Admin can amend the case and it should go out tomorrow.
Any record amended by Admin will be sent out the next day again.
